Package comp3111.coursescraper

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Controller class controls all boundary UI objects and and invokes necessary methods from other classes to manipulate data.
    Course
    Course class defines every courses scraped from the HKUST Class Schedule and Quota page.
    Filter
    Filter class handles filter-toggling and information-filtering.
    Instructor
    Instructor class defines every instructor belonging to a section.
    ListItem
    ListItem class is a container class for storing data in JavaFx TableView UI element.
    MyApplication
    The entry point of the entire program.
    Scraper
    WebScraper provide a sample code that scrape web content.
    Section
    Section class defines every sections belonging to a course.
    SFQ
    SFQ class to store sets of SFQ information scrapped from the SFQ website.
    Slot
    Slot class defines every slots belonging to a section.
    TimetableBlock
    TimetableBlock class to create blocks in Timetable tab and store block contents

    Contains: Course section ID Array of Labels storing timetable blocks of the same course section Number of blocks for the course section Array of time slots Block color assigned for the course section
